description:
GLITCH is a must see drama event from the makers of The Slap.

When Sergeant Hayes is called to Yoorana cemetery in the middle of the night, he makes a discovery that turns his world upside down - six people with no memory of their identities. Who are they and what has happened to them?

CAST: Patrick Brammall, Emma Booth, Sean Keenan, Rodger Corser, Andrew McFarlane.




Glitch - Series 1, Episode 1


When Sergeant Hayes is called to the cemetery, he makes a startling discovery. Six people have inexplicably returned from the dead and are in perfect health. How is this possible? Who are they and why are they back? #GlitchTV
